{"tid":1336557,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到熱門] 大家出發前買定回程飛，唔好臨走先買飛，只計票值唔計站架","createTime":"2019-07-21T04:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T05:39:55.000Z","uid":258270,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23f2be445a6b173cab51e437a5698cfa253f7a51","tid":1336557,"uid":258270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:22:55.000Z","msg":"港鐵單程票有效期係即日內<br />\n只要張飛係即日，咩站都入到閘<br />\n而出閘只計票值夠唔夠，所以張飛實際上係唔計地點架<br />\n<br />\n所以，假設你今日係大窩口出發，可以係入閘前，買定張去杏花邨嘅飛，而呢張飛即日內用作堅尼地城入閘去樂富都得<br />\n<br />\n我建議買張值 $15.5 過海飛 ( 市區線過海一律 $15.5 )，唔好臨走先慢吞吞買飛啦"},{"pid":"9f78784bd2f0274889838ec87695f3ee99e286f4","tid":1336557,"uid":258270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"我有野講"},{"pid":"2bc7639ef7cd8dc951aac05477e575f5322cc95f","tid":1336557,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:24:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb102cf2ba0f8cd336a51a11ced67dedef316e38","tid":1336557,"uid":60273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f78784bd2f0274889838ec87695f3ee99e286f4","tid":1336557,"uid":258270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"我有野講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"請講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188a7fb481fde6e620c36ce4d5c013772f69dbac","tid":1336557,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd67dcd66facbb76cfe3a23d2ddb7fce9947fba","tid":1336557,"uid":258270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}